CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774361472
OL,3,CMan buried woman, 33, in woods after
OL,4,Ckilling her and hiding her body under
OL,5,Cbed
OL,7,FBody cam footage shows police
OL,8,Fsearching Mohammed Durnion's flat
OL,9,Fafter a neighbour heard screams, but
OL,10,Ffailing to discover Reanne Coulson's
OL,11,Fbody.
OL,13,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter after killing a 33-year-
OL,15,Fold woman whose body was found buried
OL,16,Fin a shallow grave.
OL,18,FMohammed Durnion, 42, killed Reanne
OL,19,FCoulson at his flat in Coventry on 21
OL,20,FMay last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
