OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774361472
OL,3,CMan buried woman, 33, in woods after
OL,4,Ckilling her and hiding her body under
OL,5,Cbed
OL,7,FHe put Ms Coulson's body into a
OL,8,Fsuitcase, drove four miles to Binley
OL,9,FWoods and dug a shallow grave on a
OL,10,Fbridleway.
OL,12,FHer body was found more than three
OL,13,Fweeks later.
OL,15,FThe jury at Durnion's trial at
OL,16,FWarwickshire Justice Centre found the
OL,17,F42-year-old guilty of manslaughter and
OL,18,Fnot guilty of murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774361472
OL,3,CMan buried woman, 33, in woods after
OL,4,Ckilling her and hiding her body under
OL,5,Cbed
OL,7,FThe court was told that Ms Coulson was
OL,8,Fheard screaming and crying for help by
OL,9,Fher killer's neighbour, who called 999.
OL,11,FPolice searched the flat but failed to
OL,12,Fdiscover her body which Durnion later
OL,13,Fclaimed he'd hidden under a mattress.
OL,15,FDurnion, who worked as a labourer,
OL,16,Ftold the court that Ms Coulson died
OL,17,Ffrom an apparent overdose after a
OL,18,Fbrief argument at his flat in Paynes
OL,19,FLane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774361472
OL,3,CMan buried woman, 33, in woods after
OL,4,Ckilling her and hiding her body under
OL,5,Cbed
OL,7,FHe said he put her in a suitcase and
OL,8,Fdrove her to woodland for fear of
OL,9,Fbeing blamed for her death.
OL,11,FProsecutors claimed the 42-year-old
OL,12,Fkilled Ms Coulson in a sudden and
OL,13,Fdeliberate attack and then feigned a
OL,14,Fmental health crisis when police
OL,15,Farrived.
OL,17,FHer body wasn't found until 27 June in
OL,18,FBinley Woods - more than three weeks
OL,19,Fafter she was killed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774361472
OL,3,CMan buried woman, 33, in woods after
OL,4,Ckilling her and hiding her body under
OL,5,Cbed
OL,7,FMohammed Durnion can be seen on police
OL,8,Ffootage pointing out where he buried
OL,9,FMs Coulson.
OL,11,FHe can be heard saying, "under there."
OL,13,FHe is asked, "She's buried? How deep?"
OL,14,FHe replies, "Deep enough" and confirms
OL,15,Fhe used a shovel to dig the hole for
OL,16,Fher body.
OL,18,FDurnion will be sentenced at a later
OL,19,Fdate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
